t;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Eligibility to adjust their status and become a lawful permanent resident.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"4\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Access to certain public benefit programs and social services.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Key Requirements</h3>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">To qualify for a T Visa, you must meet the following criteria:</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"4\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Be a victim of human trafficking, including forced labor, involuntary servitude, or sexual exploitation.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Be physically present in the United States due to trafficking.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Cooperate with authorities in the investigation or prosecution of traffickers unless you are unable to do so due to trauma.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Demonstrate that returning to your home country would pose an extreme risk to your safety.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>How can we help?<span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">&nbsp;</span></h3>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">At Vasquez Law Firm, we have extensive experience representing victims of human trafficking. We guide you through every step of the process, from gathering the necessary documentation to filing your application and working closely with the relevant authorities.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Our commitment is to ensure you receive the legal and emotional support you need to overcome this difficult time and start building a secure and hopeful future.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"../contact/index.html\"><strong>Contact us today</strong></a><span data-contrast=\"auto\"> If you or someone you know needs help with the T Visa, don’t hesitate to reach out to us. At Vasquez Law Firm, we fight for you and are dedicated to protecting your rights and dignity.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Call us at 1-844-YO-PELEO <a href=\"tel:1-844-967-3536\">(1-844-967-3536).</a></span></p></div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t</div>\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t</article>\n\n\t\t\t\n\n",
